<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>Conversión de Temperatura - Monsters Inc</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        html, body {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Comic Sans MS', cursive, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8EE3EF, #A281D7);
            background-image: url('/images/sulli.jpg'); /* fondo Sulley */
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .monster-home {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 800px;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            color: #FFD700;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px #000;
        }

        label {
            color: #eee;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .btn-primary, .btn-warning {
            background-color: #5D9CEC;
            border: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

            .btn-primary:hover, .btn-warning:hover {
                background-color: #4A89DC;
            }

        .alert-danger {
            background-color: #e74c3c;
            border: none;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .boo-img {
            max-width: 200px;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .monster-explanation {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #f1c40f;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        .conversion-section {
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="monster-home">
        <h1>🎓 CONVERSIÓN UNIDADES MONSTER G02</h1>

        <!-- Formulario: Celsius a Fahrenheit -->
        <div class="conversion-section">
            <form action="/Home/ConvertToFahrenheit" method="post">
                <label for="celsius">👾 Ingresar Celsius:</label>
                <input type="text" name="celsius" id="celsius" required class="form-control my-2" />
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Convertir a °F</button>
            </form>
            <p>@ViewBag.FahrenheitResult</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Formulario: Fahrenheit a Celsius -->
        <div class="conversion-section">
            <form action="/Home/ConvertToCelsius" method="post">
                <label for="fahrenheit">👾 Ingresar Fahrenheit:</label>
                <input type="text" name="fahrenheit" id="fahrenheit" required class="form-control my-2" />
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Convertir a °C</button>
            </form>
            <p>@ViewBag.CelsiusResult</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Botón de Cerrar Sesión -->
        <div class="conversion-section">
            <form action="/Home/Logout" method="get">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-warning">Cerrar Sesión</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Modal de Boo -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="booModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="booModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered modal-lg">
            <div class="modal-content" style="background-color: #2c3e50; color: #f1c40f;">
                <div class="modal-header border-0">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="booModalLabel">👧 Hola, soy Boo!</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Cerrar"></button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body d-flex align-items-center">
                    <img class="boo-img me-3" src="~/images/buu.jpg" alt="Boo" />
                    <div class="monster-explanation">
                        <p>¡Hoy te voy a ayudar a convertir entre Celsius y Fahrenheit. ¡Es super fácil!</p>
                        <p>Si tienes grados Celsius, simplemente haz clic en "Convertir a °F", y si tienes grados Fahrenheit, haz lo mismo para convertirlo a °C.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripts de Bootstrap y activación del modal -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        window.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
            const modalShown = sessionStorage.getItem('booModalShown');
            if (!modalShown) {
                const booModal = new bootstrap.Modal(document.getElementById('booModal'));
                booModal.show();
                sessionStorage.setItem('booModalShown', 'true');
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
